          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PS",
                "PROPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "The scattered alpha particles were momentum",
                "analyzed with a Q3D spectrograph and detected by a",
                "position sensitive proportional counter. Particle",
                "identification was done by using the dE signal from",
                "the proportional counter and an E signal from  a",
                "plastic scintillator attached to a lightguide."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 90Zr and 96Zr targets were self-supporting metal",
                "foils. The mean target thicknesses of 0.520 mg/cm2 and",
                "0.540 mg/cm2 for 90Zr and 96Zr, respectively, were",
                "obtained.",
                "Isotopic composition of the targets:",
                "Isotope              Abundance (%)",
                "           90Zr target           96Zr target",
                "90Zr       97.65+-0.1            7.25+-0.1",
                "91Zr       0.96+-0.05            1.41+-0.05",
                "92Zr       0.71+-0.05            2.24+-0.05",
                "94Zr       0.55+-0.05            3.85+-0.05",
                "96Zr       0.13+-0.05            82.25+-0.1",
                "The target thicknesses were determined from energy loss",
                "measurements with an 241Am alpha-source. The absolute",
                "accuracy of this method was +-10%, while the relative",
                "normalization was found to be consistent within 1%."
              ]
            }
          ],
